<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p><em>Summary:</em>
Zend_Gdata_Extension_OriginalEvent does not include support for Zend_Gdata_Extension_When as a child element.</p>

<p><em>Steps to Reproduce:</em>
1. Create a new Zend_Gdata_Extension_OriginalEvent using the following XML snippet:</p>

<pre class="literal">&lt;?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?&gt;
</pre>

<p><em>Expected Results:</em>
The {{when}} element should be converted to a first-class {{Zend_Gdata_Extension_When}} property of the original {{Zned_Gdata_Extension_OriginalEvent}} instance.</p>

<p><em>Actual Results:</em>
The {{when}} element is instead converted to an extension element.</p>

<p><em>Regression:</em>
Introduced in r4878, affects 1.0.0 RC1 and RC2.</p>

<p><em>Notes:</em>
Patch sent to rboyd for review.</p>

